          "room_name": "Deluxe Room",
          "created": "2024-10-22T16:33:16.194726Z",
          "description": "MJ Funcity is the best water park in Lucknow. It is the perfect place to spend a day out with family and friends. The park has a wide range of attractions, including a lazy river, a wave pool, a diving area, and more. If you’re looking for an amusement park that offers something for everyone, MJ Funcity is the place to go. It is the best theme park in Lucknow. It has a lot of rides and attractions for all ages. It’s also a great place to take your family on summer days. There’s something for everyone, from small children’s rides to thrilling thrill rides. The park is also well-equipped with food stalls and vendors, making it easy for you to buy snacks or meals to take with you on your ride.",
